{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to become the hero of cleanliness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the POOBO universe, you are a tiny and cute poop trying to escape the toilet and survive! Fight against hundreds, even thousands of bacteria while creating the ultimate weapon combinations to claim victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Choose Your Character!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/character.png?t=1737708921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Equip Your First Weapon!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/choose_your_weapon.gif?t=1737708921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the start of the game, you\u2019ll need to make an important decision: choose your first weapon! Each weapon has unique abilities\u2014some are great for close combat, while others help you defeat enemies from a distance. You can carry up to 6 weapons, so plan strategically and pick your first weapon to begin your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Level Up! Upgrade Your Abilities.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/levelup.gif?t=1737708921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ve leveled up! Each level gives you the chance to make your character even stronger. Choose a card to enhance your stats! If you don\u2019t get the abilities you\u2019re looking for, you can reshuffle the cards and try again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Equip New Weapons!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/Store.png?t=1737708921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can equip up to 6 weapons and 6 items at the same time. Each round gives you a chance to renew and upgrade your arsenal. Make the right choices to boost your power and dominate your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Upgrade Your Weapons!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/Upgrade.png?t=1737708921\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enhance your weapons and items in your inventory to increase your strength. To do this, you\u2019ll need at least 2 of the same weapon or item. With each upgrade, you\u2019ll grow stronger and gain an edge against your enemies!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Apprentice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2989730/781a8dcef54622399fd0575ab1a1c13c903c8a46.jpg"},{"name":"Skilled","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2989730/89b7dd3a3f58f467b3f059e5bd33ccf54b8892fa.jpg"},{"name":"Expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2989730/7f1f9f744f7e9f086bb4ed119f44143d4c4325ea.jpg"},{"name":"Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2989730/3cb07ad0d13d753f7c8691c4045dd68a91746b20.jpg"},{"name":"Veteran","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2989730/3ea7a6d858908c7f7c5652757ed5b904461c0c09.jpg"},{"name":"Elite","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2989730/bd0c05beaf84f0bf80a0bea267862e4601dd663c.jpg"},{"name":"Brutal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2989730/5f051b9308483e1fbb42eb08fb0d56154b8e7243.jpg"},{"name":"Legendary","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/